### Point 4: AI-Generated Career Roadmap
### ============================================

### Generate a personalized learning roadmap
POST http://localhost:3000/api/ai/roadmap
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tech_stack": "DevOps Engineering",
  "provider": "gemini",
  "include_current_skills": true
}

###

### Get all saved roadmaps for user
GET http://localhost:3000/api/ai/roadmaps
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

### Get specific roadmap by ID (replace {id} with actual roadmap_id)
